Taarifa is an online platform for crowd

sourced reporting and triaging of infrastructure related issues. It is a platform which allows

citizens to engage with the government and register their issues with the local infrastructure of

their area. This project aims to analyze the data collected by Taarifa and the Tanzanian Ministry

of Water.

The data was pre processed for removing redundant attributes, dimentionality reduction and inconsistent data removal.
Implemented RANDOM FOREST, DEEP LEARNING, ADABOOST and LOGISTIC REGRESSION classifiers using the scikit learn library in python.
The result was an 80% accuracy on the test data.
